      "updated": 1776043891317,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Bootstrapping [If needed]\n\n- Azure Landing Zones\n- Capacity Planning CIDR range for Hub & Spoke\n- Management Group Setup\n- IAM for creating/patching Self-Hosted Runner\nInfra\n- Build Vnets\n- Build Network topology of Hub & Spoke\n- Put WAF setup on Hub (basic FQDN setup)\n- Put DNS Registry if needed on Hub\n- Runner ACR\n- Runner Infra [VM or Containers]\n- Test Deploy basic workload [Storage Account,\nKey Vault, Azure Configuration Manager with nsg]\n ",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Bootstrapping [If needed]\n\n- Azure Landing Zones\n- Capacity Planning CIDR range for Hub & Spoke\n- Management Group Setup\n- IAM for creating/patching Self-Hosted Runner\nInfra\n- Build Vnets\n- Build Network topology of Hub & Spoke\n- Put WAF setup on Hub (basic FQDN setup)\n- Put DNS Registry if needed on Hub\n- Runner ACR\n- Runner Infra [VM or Containers]\n- Test Deploy basic workload [Storage Account,\nKey Vault, Azure Configuration Manager with nsg]\n ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
