      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776039711524,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Phase 1 - Foundation \n\nCreate IAC Repo\n- Databricks workspace (dev first)\n- Cluster policies (basic)\n- RBAC Access Model\n\nStand up Dev Environment\n\nDefine repoistory strategy\nSplit repos for pipelines (per domain/workload)\n\nIntroduce basic CI pipeline\n- Linting & unit test for pipeline code\n\nImplement Manual Deployment to DB via CI\n\nBaseline Monitoring & Logging\n\n",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Phase 1 - Foundation \n\nCreate IAC Repo\n- Databricks workspace (dev first)\n- Cluster policies (basic)\n- RBAC Access Model\n\nStand up Dev Environment\n\nDefine repoistory strategy\nSplit repos for pipelines (per domain/workload)\n\nIntroduce basic CI pipeline\n- Linting & unit test for pipeline code\n\nImplement Manual Deployment to DB via CI\n\nBaseline Monitoring & Logging\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
