      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776027781053,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Install Gitops on each Cluster\n- Argo CD from platform mono repo\n- Create base namespace & shared platform services\n- Define cluster add-ons as Git-managed\n    - ingress/Gateway\n    - cert handling\n    - external secrets/ kv integration\n   - policy agents\n   - observability agents",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Install Gitops on each Cluster\n- Argo CD from platform mono repo\n- Create base namespace & shared platform services\n- Define cluster add-ons as Git-managed\n    - ingress/Gateway\n    - cert handling\n    - external secrets/ kv integration\n   - policy agents\n   - observability agents",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
