      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776029137045,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Phase 4 - Migrate Workload into AKS \n\nWAVE 1 - Stateless low-risk services\n- APIs\n- Internal services\n- simple workers\n\nParameters \n- easier to containerise\n- lowest migration risk\n- proves the path\n\nSteps\n- containerise app\n- externalise application config\n- move secrets to vault via ksm workflows\n- define k8 deployment + service\n- deploy to dev\n- validate in stg\n- promote to prod\n\nWAVE 2 - Scheduled jobs & on-prem schedulers\n- cron tasks\n- periodic workers\n\nTarget Platform\n- AKS Cron Jobs\n\nSteps\n- isolate job logic\n- containerize job\n- create CronJob spec\n- define concurrency & retry\n- add mertrics/alerting\n- deploy via GitOps",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Phase 4 - Migrate Workload into AKS \n\nWAVE 1 - Stateless low-risk services\n- APIs\n- Internal services\n- simple workers\n\nParameters \n- easier to containerise\n- lowest migration risk\n- proves the path\n\nSteps\n- containerise app\n- externalise application config\n- move secrets to vault via ksm workflows\n- define k8 deployment + service\n- deploy to dev\n- validate in stg\n- promote to prod\n\nWAVE 2 - Scheduled jobs & on-prem schedulers\n- cron tasks\n- periodic workers\n\nTarget Platform\n- AKS Cron Jobs\n\nSteps\n- isolate job logic\n- containerize job\n- create CronJob spec\n- define concurrency & retry\n- add mertrics/alerting\n- deploy via GitOps",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
