    {
      "id": "9SslPVZsNrovBVbwEayOJ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5183.922838948853,
      "y": 1321.9084679629027,
      "width": 1073.771728515625,
      "height": 1440,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b8e",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1554001697,
      "version": 749,
      "versionNonce": 88865615,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776029660927,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Phase 5 - Enviornment Promotion Model\n\nDev\n- rapid integration\n- frequent deploy\n- test the packaging & runtime model\n\nFlow\n- merge to main\n- image pushed\n- Gitops auto-updates dev or aut-sync dev branch/tag\n\n\nStaging\n- prod like verification\n- smoke tests\n- dependency validation\n\nFlow\n- promote same immutable artifact\n- no rebuild\n- change cluster-config repo to new approved version\n- GitOps reconciles cluster\n\nProd\n- manual approval to update prod desired state in Git\n- GitOps reconciles prod\n- optional progressive strategy based on conventional commit\n  - rolling\n  - canary\n  - blue/green\n- breaking changes means load balancing to be considered",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Phase 5 - Enviornment Promotion Model\n\nDev\n- rapid integration\n- frequent deploy\n- test the packaging & runtime model\n\nFlow\n- merge to main\n- image pushed\n- Gitops auto-updates dev or aut-sync dev branch/tag\n\n\nStaging\n- prod like verification\n- smoke tests\n- dependency validation\n\nFlow\n- promote same immutable artifact\n- no rebuild\n- change cluster-config repo to new approved version\n- GitOps reconciles cluster\n\nProd\n- manual approval to update prod desired state in Git\n- GitOps reconciles prod\n- optional progressive strategy based on conventional commit\n  - rolling\n  - canary\n  - blue/green\n- breaking changes means load balancing to be considered",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
